summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the dismissal of certain parcels of land from that certain proceeding for the condemnation, appropriation and taking of land and other property necessary for pipe line right of way across the southeast quarter of the southwest quarter of Section 9, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M., as provided for in Ordinance No. 56125, being Cause No. 22336 in the Superior Court of the State of Washington, for King County.
